{"lastModified":1758271513477,"uri":"c::18264259421::vessel::8e7e76a0-704d-11ef-bd73-e5c889f41a1c","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Base / Home Port: Alyki Port Paros, Greece\nOperating Area: Greece\n\nDiscover the beauty of Paros island and its surroundings on our luxurious Sailor's Boat Poseidon. The Saxdor 320 GTO, with Italian design, American functionality, and German quality, offers both luxury and sportiness, ensuring a high level of comfort during your daily cruises in Paros.\n\nEmbark on a private boat rental adventure, visiting nearby islands such as Mykonos, Koufonisia, Irakleia, Shoinousa, Sifnos, and Milos. Explore the stunning Blue Lagoon beach, the mesmerizing Caves of Antiparos, and the secluded Despotiko island.\n\nThe Poseidon offers plenty of space for lounging, featuring an extended sunpad on the foredeck and a convertible dinette for sunbathing. The opposed seating can also become forward-facing benches when cruising at speeds up to 50 knots, thanks to the 300hp twin engines.\n\nWhen stationary, the two folding platforms provide additional space. Enjoy a meal at the onboard lunch table, complete with a sink, fridge, freezer, and a top-notch Fusion sound system to enhance your sea transfer experience. The interior includes a cozy double bed and a fully equipped toilet for maximum convenience during your Blue Lagoon cruise or a trip to the Antiparos caves.","blueprint":{"name":"POSEIDON","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::8e7e76a0-704d-11ef-bd73-e5c889f41a1c::assets::16637830-15ef-11f0-89d5-f1b015925c7b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8e7e76a0-704d-11ef-bd73-e5c889f41a1c::assets::16866981-15ef-11f0-89d5-f1b015925c7b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8e7e76a0-704d-11ef-bd73-e5c889f41a1c::assets::16866980-15ef-11f0-89d5-f1b015925c7b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::8e7e76a0-704d-11ef-bd73-e5c889f41a1c::assets::16888c60-15ef-11f0-89d5-f1b015925c7b/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::ves